data.description: Pretty 2 bedroom cape cod in Move-In condition! Lovely front porch, beautiful wood flooring in the first floor LR, BR & hall. Great eat-in kitchen is updated and features built-ins - all appliances stay. Second floor has a huge bedroom. Home is freshly painted and squeaky clean. Yard is fenced and features a large parking apron in the back and one car garage under the home. Great location on this no outlet street! All of this plus a beautifully manicured yard makes you proud to call this "Home"
